OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1773947499
OL,3,CWorker awarded #8,000 after police dog
OL,4,Cattack
OL,6,FA man who was attacked by a police dog
OL,7,Fwhile working for the same force has
OL,8,Fbeen awarded #8,000 over the physical
OL,9,Fand mental harm he suffered.
OL,11,FNetwork design engineer Patrick Bryant
OL,12,Fwas in a wiring room at a police
OL,13,Fstation in Hull when the dog lunged at
OL,14,Fhim, causing him wounds to his arm,
OL,15,Ffinger and knee.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,370,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1773947499
OL,3,CWorker awarded #8,000 after police dog
OL,4,Cattack
OL,6,FThe 43-year-old father-of-four, who
OL,7,Fwas employed by South Yorkshire Police
OL,8,Fat the time but was working as a
OL,9,Fcontractor for Humberside Police, said
OL,10,Fhe still struggles with psychological
OL,11,Fissues two years after the incident.
OL,13,FHe said: "I've got a Labrador who
OL,14,Fwouldn't hurt a fly, but, even now, I
OL,15,Fstill get occasionally anxious when he
OL,16,Fmakes a sudden movement or jumps on to
OL,17,Fthe sofa.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,370,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1773947499
OL,3,CWorker awarded #8,000 after police dog
OL,4,Cattack
OL,6,F"I'm dubious about all dogs now and
OL,7,Falways cross to the other side of the
OL,8,Froad when I see one coming towards me
OL,9,Fwith their owner."
OL,11,FThe dog was off the leash when it was
OL,12,Ftaking part in training with a
OL,13,Fhandler, who had assumed the building
OL,14,Fon Hessle Road was empty, in March
OL,15,F2024.
OL,17,FMr Bryant said the police station was
OL,18,F"like a ghost town" because Humberside
OL,19,FPolice was vacating the site.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,370,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1773947499
OL,3,CWorker awarded #8,000 after police dog
OL,4,Cattack
OL,6,FHe said: "I was in the communication
OL,7,Froom with a third-party telephone
OL,8,Fengineer when I heard a noise at the
OL,9,Fdoor. It sounded like someone shouting.
OL,11,F"We'd been in there for an hour and a
OL,12,Fhalf and I was waiting for someone to
OL,13,Ftake over ` I just thought it was him.
OL,15,F"I opened the door and the dog just
OL,16,Ftook off and went for me. I didn't
OL,17,Fhave a clue how to react, but it felt
OL,18,Fsavage at the time and I was very,
OL,19,Fvery scared ` as anyone would be."
OL,26,@{D@bO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,370,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1773947499
OL,3,CWorker awarded #8,000 after police dog
OL,4,Cattack
OL,6,FThe force admitted liability and
OL,7,Fawarded Mr Bryant #8,000 in
OL,8,Fcompensation.
OL,10,FBut he says he has not had an apology.
OL,12,F"The only thing I got from them,
OL,13,Funbelievably, was an offer to go out
OL,14,Fwith the dog-handling team and the dog
OL,15,Fthat bit me for a training session to
OL,16,Fsee how it all works," he said.
OL,18,F"Needless to say, I turned that one
OL,19,Fdown. It's not about the money. I just
OL,20,Fwanted an apology."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,370,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1773947499
OL,3,CWorker awarded #8,000 after police dog
OL,4,Cattack
OL,6,FSarah Summers, of Hudgell Solicitors,
OL,7,Fwho represented Mr Bryant, said the
OL,8,Fattack "could have had far more
OL,9,Fprofound consequences".
OL,11,F"Had the dog not been dragged off
OL,12,FPatrick as soon as possible, his
OL,13,Finjuries would have been far more
OL,14,Fsevere," she said.
OL,16,F"Patrick was badly let down by
OL,17,FHumberside Police on numerous levels `
OL,18,Fthe most striking of which being a
OL,19,Fcomplete ignorance to think anyone was
OL,20,Fin the building at the time.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,370,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1773947499
OL,3,CWorker awarded #8,000 after police dog
OL,4,Cattack
OL,6,F"At the bare minimum, employers should
OL,7,Foffer members of staff a safe place of
OL,8,Fwork.
OL,10,F"That he was even allowed to come into
OL,11,Fcontact with a police dog is an utter
OL,12,Fbreach of duty of care."
OL,14,FIn a statement, Humberside Police said
OL,15,Fthe safety of workers, was a
OL,16,F"priority".
OL,18,FIt said the site was a dedicated dog
OL,19,Ftraining facility and officers had
OL,20,Fsearched the building to ensure no one
OL,21,Fwas inside.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,370,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1773947499
OL,3,CWorker awarded #8,000 after police dog
OL,4,Cattack
OL,6,FA spokesperson said: "A full review of
OL,7,Fthe incident was completed, resulting
OL,8,Fin strengthened on-site measures,
OL,9,Fincluding additional signage at the
OL,10,Ffront of the building to reinforce
OL,11,Fexisting controls, and ensure whoever
OL,12,Fis scheduled to be on site is aware of
OL,13,Fpolice dog training exercises in
OL,14,Fprogress."
OL,16,FThe incident was referred to the
OL,17,FIndependent Office for Police Conduct
OL,18,F(IOPC), but no further action was
OL,19,Ftaken.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
